{"tid":186822,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中文卷二作文最後提示！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2017-04-04T13:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T23:41:54.000Z","uid":7119,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e057215c0fee678853ac2b43d47ba207e184b58","tid":186822,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:05:04.000Z","msg":"想穩３以上既千祈唔好作描寫／記敘文　<br />\n上年好多人都掌握唔到個技巧同扣唔中題炒哂車<br />\n所以其實第一條題目係好伏，想穩就唔好搏<br />\n<br />\n想３以上既宜家拿拿林背幾個必用例子聽日作議論文<br />\n其實同通識既論文框架差唔多　定義係入題時落就最易既<br />\n最最最緊要記得標題句後交待兩至三句背景再比例子<br />\n每段都咁作既話肯定過一千字　<br />\n<br />\n希望大家中文順順利利入到Ｕ<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c69fbca4622d580b49b214143bccecd306c466","tid":186822,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:07:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f17c29333f1bd5a22a418dca93dd11f7dd457d","tid":186822,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63218b7b9475d58c82f5f9a08754087851418e46","tid":186822,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e42b96286fb4a95771a8b953c70ca4d80450538","tid":186822,"uid":34,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:13:18.000Z","msg":"ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72095d3c8619f2a2c98308b0a9b9b212092280e5","tid":186822,"uid":70763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5fdfe64eb50ed7659836e163d6a7185f161f01","tid":186822,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:22:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0f7adb7a7f67fa707c2fdb79db6f72af5c967b5","tid":186822,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你估一定有議論文咩..2012 pp有, 但正式就一條都冇<br />\nHKEAA 好古惑㗎點會話畀你知一定出邊幾類題呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2012刺猬咪就係議論文，當然你要自己領會段文字，然後轉化到含義，先寫得出篇文。<br />\n<br />\n其實冇話一定議論文容易扣題，考評班魔鬼向來奉行題目越簡單，就越多伏。<br />\n<br />\n佢如果直接出條題目叫你議論咩咩，我建議你最好唔揀添。"},{"pid":"7606168d6dc83e2eedd7882580e54cd69ae1138e","tid":186822,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:27:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你估一定有議論文咩..2012 pp有, 但正式就一條都冇<br />\nHKEAA 好古惑㗎點會話畀你知一定出邊幾類題呀</blockquote><br />\n刺猬"},{"pid":"e75892d228f042f95c17f1bdcddba821a71a80b3","tid":186822,"uid":74335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:28:21.000Z","msg":"大概ge框架係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a1a47ac273fd55c85177e499e84dc978d69236","tid":186822,"uid":13816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:30:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e9e568629cd0e262ae0681b73e710f69722d71d","tid":186822,"uid":7119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大概ge框架係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我正文有提過<br />\n<br />\n正論大概係Topicsentence之後背景(可以係現今社會問題/current problem)<br />\n再加例子,之後扣返落自己個point 度再做小結<br />\n<br />\n其實同通識真係好似 文筆寫好d就得"},{"pid":"77ba97814cef66b662d784477a84bda2be60b625","tid":186822,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T13:45:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大概ge框架係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我正文有提過<br />\n<br />\n正論大概係Topicsentence之後背景(可以係現今社會問題/current problem)<br />\n再加例子,之後扣返落自己個point 度再做小結<br />\n<br />\n其實同通識真係好似 文筆寫好d就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你寫唔到中國文化元素落去，當通識咁考一定死硬。<br />\n<br />\n反而作記敘描寫抒情咁，真係有故仔就可以不知不覺滲入中國文化元素，唔一定要拋到書包。"},{"pid":"f625453ddb668f31665b829bd5ef78471d16a1e9","tid":186822,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:02:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大概ge框架係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我正文有提過<br />\n<br />\n正論大概係Topicsentence之後背景(可以係現今社會問題/current problem)<br />\n再加例子,之後扣返落自己個point 度再做小結<br />\n<br />\n其實同通識真係好似 文筆寫好d就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你寫唔到中國文化元素落去，當通識咁考一定死硬。<br />\n<br />\n反而作記敘描寫抒情咁，真係有故仔就可以不知不覺滲入中國文化元素，唔一定要拋到書包。</blockquote><br />\n其實題目一定會有中化字眼 所以我冇專登講 剩係話要扣"},{"pid":"06a89af4218c9fc271fd1c8c1e6421aa435c56fb","tid":186822,"uid":74335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:04:52.000Z","msg":"靜係不停用舉例論證得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d481ec9e5770fe89b85f1742c8755b287e5263","tid":186822,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:12:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靜係不停用舉例論證得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最好唔好，其實例字唔洗太多但係point角度要夠闊"},{"pid":"be00608c30d33fa791eb7f3ce4f07aa07ffd7e39","tid":186822,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:13:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>靜係不停用舉例論證得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最好唔好，其實例子唔洗太多但係point角度要夠闊</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ebf2b0a71740fc0fd1e349f32ac803d7b0c2e601","tid":186822,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4466437a29ff78a57e9d5d307d0ea4ba3a6723c","tid":186822,"uid":96262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T21:44:56.000Z","msg":"尋晚掙扎左好耐今日究竟寫咩文好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該穩陣起見都係議論了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 謝樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b419e481dcb78d8fdb9366c62e26dfa7bfb7f8","tid":186822,"uid":35190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T23:41:54.000Z","msg":"平時寫開邊類就寫邊類，考試先轉好易食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}